metadata.name: Hybrid Humans
metadata.description: The HyHu Network is a first of it's kind and consists of multiple Ecosystems tied back to an amazing NFT at the centre. All Ecosystems will be independently revenue-generating and consistently funding Holders benefits through an array of interesting and intertwined Utilities. The Genesis NFT collection consists of 1,111 HybridHumans with unique benefits only available to collection holders.
